{"tid":2311701,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"渣哥同龍門都只不過係生意人","createTime":"2020-12-04T09:30:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T08:49:37.000Z","uid":37038,"like":5,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1a6a8813acca322f47005f025ad0f013462acbbe","tid":2311701,"uid":37038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T09:30:11.000Z","msg":"系呢個時勢開咁多舖頭<br />\n你話唔想搵錢唔會有人信<br />\n亦都唔洗講佢地係偽黃定真黃<br />\n<br />\n渣哥係咩人識佢既人都知<br />\n當初同謝振中fd 到搭曬膊頭<br />\n到有難果時第一個割蓆<br />\n為既係要喺呢個時勢賺到最多既錢<br />\n呢種人頂多都只係生意人<br />\n佢以前做生意 又飲酒玩女<br />\n係點既人根本唔洗多講<br />\n<br />\n龍門張俊傑都唔洗多講<br />\n又係一個醒目仔<br />\n但香港人唔係蠢<br />\n呃得香港人一時呃唔到一世<br />\n<br />\n佢地識得包裝 <br />\n識得marketing<br />\n但香港人唔係要呢d<br />\n喺香港賺錢搵錢就係原罪<br />\n因為香港已經唔係你想搵錢就搵到<br />\n幾多公司最尾可以唔俾紅色資本收購同化"},{"pid":"cdc6e506ad47b57905cf1e98edd314bcd81d4480","tid":2311701,"uid":810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T09:33:49.000Z","msg":"系"},{"pid":"f3de124794b7930b23473f7a80bc0b2f0ab9595c","tid":2311701,"uid":361975,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T09:35:09.000Z","msg":"睇到你第一個字大大隻<span class=\"red\">系</span><br />\n後面已經冇睇落去"},{"pid":"3030c91f4a211fa97e3cf46745c356501f6f7994","tid":2311701,"uid":35924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T10:59:49.000Z","msg":"Topic 個係岩，但內文就用系姐係點"},{"pid":"db80b732e8da239cf831e8b760b7a28705df8bdb","tid":2311701,"uid":316590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T12:31:12.000Z","msg":"但渣狗一定係狗先"},{"pid":"d24bada6195214fa87c54d2c4b7cdfc3e65e838b","tid":2311701,"uid":109570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T12:33:23.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"364756aed9c37e3fb8ee29d88fc9a01a5477faab","tid":2311701,"uid":2210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T13:17:24.000Z","msg":"打個和算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />